About the Author

Neil Matthew and has been programming UNIX systems since 1978. Neil started with Linux back in 1993 and is currently working to encourage businesses to adopt Linux for their key systems. With an IT career spanning 20 years including wired and radio communications and technology consultancy, Neil is currently working as a Systems Architect for Celesio, a European multi-national pharmaceutical wholesaler and retailer.
